Patch Set 2: Workflow-1

Hi,

As per promised in the glance weekly meeting [1], we have come up with a patch to synced policy framework in glance.

We will follow a process and file a new blueprint for this in K release, and once the K release starts we will submit this patch immediately.

Till then please have a look at the design and let me know your suggestions if any.

[1] http://eavesdrop.openstack.org/meetings/glance/2014/glance.2014-08-28-14.11.log.html
